OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F146A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCReflections on this week's
OL,4,Cplayout incident on BBC Scotland
OL,5,
OL,6,FWithin seconds a slide would appear.
OL,7,FThen came the familiar, reassuring
OL,8,Fvoice of the announcer to apologise
OL,9,Ffollowed by some music.
OL,11,FIf the fault was likely to last for
OL,12,Fsome time, a filler programme could be
OL,13,Ftaken from the shelf.
OL,15,FIn the nations and regions there was an
OL,16,Fadded risk.
OL,18,FWhat if the network link broke down or
OL,19,Fsuddenly started carrying the wrong
OL,20,Fmaterial?
OL,23,EPub: 22-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,147,140,200,120,0,100
