OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F146A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G9/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCReflections on this week's
OL,4,Cplayout incident on BBC Scotland
OL,5,
OL,6,FPlaying out BBC One or Two is not like
OL,7,Fplaying out a minor satellite channel.
OL,9,FBBC Presentation used to symbolise all
OL,10,Fthat was best in the corporation's
OL,11,Fprofessionalism in an age when things
OL,12,Fwent wrong far more frequently.
OL,14,FWith the right resilience arrangements,
OL,15,Fit could again.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
